<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just the same as always. 
Completely normal.</i></font>

9
00:00:33,010 --> 00:00:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I guess it would be. 
That's how it works, right?</i></font>

10
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:39,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="16"><font color="#ffffff">{\an8}CLASS TRIP</font></font></font></font>

