<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="16"><font color="#ffffff">GROUP ACTIVITIES</font></font></font></font>

17
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:39,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="16"><font color="#ffffff">NARA
DAY 2</font></font></font></font>

18
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:39,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="16"><font color="#ffffff">DAY 3
OSAKA</font></font></font></font>

19
00:00:36,850 --> 00:00:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, that's the general schedule 
I'd like to work with.</font>

20
00:00:40,230 --> 00:00:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And groups will have free time,</font>

21
00:00:42,810 --> 00:00:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so think about where you want to go.</font>

22
00:00:44,940 --> 00:00:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll hand out the group 
and room assignments later.</font>

23
00:00:53,530 --> 00:00:57,040
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24"><font color="#ffffff">CLASS TRIP</font></font></font></font>

24
00:00:53,530 --> 00:00:57,040
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24"><font color="#ffffff">OBJECTIVES</font></font></font></font>

25
00:00:53,990 --> 00:00:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Class Trip Arc begins now!</font>

26
00:01:09,470 --> 00:01:14,260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial">{\an8}YOU AND I ARE POLAR OPPOSITES</font></b></font>

27
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#585755"><font size="16">CLASS TRIP GUIDE</font></font></b></font>

28
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#585755"><font size="16">YEAR 2 CLASS</font></font></b></font>

29
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:29,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#d0dfdd">KYOTO</font></font></b></font>

30
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, guys.</font>

31
00:02:29,210 --> 00:02:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This should be class rep work.</font>

32
00:02:29,210 --> 00:02:32,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font face="Arial"><font size="16">EVERYONE IN THE
GOING-HOME CLUB</font></font></font>

33
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It'll go faster if we all pitch in, right?</font>

34
00:02:32,970 --> 00:02:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna ker-chack the mega stapler!</font>

35
00:02:34,930 --> 00:02:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So sloppy!</font>

36
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:38,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#585755"><font size="24">KONEKO PREFECTURAL
HIGH SCHOOL</font></font></b></font>

37
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:38,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#585755"><font size="24">CLASS TRIP GUIDE</font></font></b></font>

38
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:38,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#585755"><font size="24">YEAR 2 CLASS</font></font></b></font>

39
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:40,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f2ffb5"><font size="28">{\an8}QUIET FOCUS...</font></font></b></font>

40
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:43,480
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"></font></b><font size="20">DEAD-END
PIECE</font></font>

41
00:02:48,150 --> 00:02:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for making you help me, Nisshi.</font>

42
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. I actually like 
doing simple tasks like this.</font>

43
00:02:53,820 --> 00:02:54,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so nice.</font>

44
00:02:54,990 --> 00:03:03,580
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ea9950"><font size="24">{\an8}MUTTER MUTTER MUTTER</font></font></b></font>

45
00:02:54,990 --> 00:02:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, when people say, 
"I have club activities"?</font>

46
00:02:57,700 --> 00:03:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's treated like a perfect excuse, 
but are clubs that special?</font>

47
00:03:00,410 --> 00:03:03,580
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f1df97"><font size="16">2-8 CLASS REPS</font></font></b></font>

48
00:03:00,450 --> 00:03:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can't, 
then don't be a class rep, right?</font>

49
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it just for your résumé?</font>

50
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I despise people who only seem
to have it together and skate by.</font>

51
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:14,260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#a01004"><font size="28">CRACKLE...</font></font></b></font>

52
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behind their dazzling lives, 
someone else is doing the work,</font>

53
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:12,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but no one pictures that, do they?</font>

54
00:03:12,050 --> 00:03:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hon-chan, calm down.</font>

55
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll put on a video of a funny 
comedy I watched last night.</font>

56
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:17,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Then they slowly 
turned around and said...</i></font>

57
00:03:17,510 --> 00:03:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It was you!</i></font>

58
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:19,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ec518f"><font size="16">HEE HEE...</font></font></b></font>

59
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get it.</i></font>

60
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Nisshi, do you have 
any recent fun stories?</font>

61
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What about the video?</font>

62
00:03:26,390 --> 00:03:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any progress since you said 
you didn't know how you felt?</font>

63
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Yamada.</font>

64
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

65
00:03:31,270 --> 00:03:32,020
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#b7ff85">JOLT</font></font></font></b></font>

66
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, that's... Well...</font>

67
00:03:35,950 --> 00:03:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I probably—</font>

68
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two are doing all that?</font>

69
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:41,780
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ea1587"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="28"><i>{\an9}WAAAAAAH</i></font></font></font></b></font>

70
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada!</font>

71
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What? Why?</font>

72
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,790
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font face="Arial"><font color="#f9f9f9">Day 1</font></font></font></b></font>

73
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,790
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font face="Arial"><font color="#f9f9f9">Day 2</font></font></font></b></font>

74
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Isn't it exhausting doing that 
by yourselves?</font>

75
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got about eight of us working on it.</font>

76
00:03:44,830 --> 00:03:46,540
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20"><font color="#f8ffaa">QUICK QUICK QUICK</font></font></font></b></font>

77
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds like too many, doesn't it?</font>

78
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I'm just an extra body.</font>

79
00:03:51,170 --> 00:03:51,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lolz.</font>

80
00:03:52,170 --> 00:03:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, why don't you help us over here?</font>

81
00:03:54,050 --> 00:03:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to me!</font>

82
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:57,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, go ahead and fold all that paper.</font>

83
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will do!</font>

84
00:04:01,510 --> 00:04:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, for the groups, should it be decided 
by lottery, or should we get to pick?</font>

85
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be better 
if we got to pick, right?</font>

86
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, most people probably 
feel that way.</font>

87
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Depending on how many 
can be in a group,</font>

88
00:04:12,060 --> 00:04:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet there'll be some awkward pairings.</font>

89
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, what do you think?</font>

90
00:04:15,570 --> 00:04:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

91
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

92
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does "yeah" mean?</font>

93
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weren't listening, were you?</font>

94
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's with this vibe? 
Are they in the middle of a fight?</i></font>

95
00:04:29,290 --> 00:04:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How much of your trip do you 
have planned in your class?</font>

96
00:04:32,710 --> 00:04:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aside from activities for the whole class.</font>

97
00:04:34,380 --> 00:04:39,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, we've divided into groups, 
and the groups are deciding where to go.</font>

98
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Then you've gotten farther than us.</font>

99
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

100
00:04:43,930 --> 00:04:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nisshi is able to talk more than before.</i></font>

101
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They've got a nice atmosphere going.</i></font>

102
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Keep it up, Nisshi!</i></font>

103
00:04:50,350 --> 00:04:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just consider me invisible right now.</i></font>

104
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:53,360
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#54adc1"></font></b>SHFF...</font>

105
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gapacho said they're already 
discussing their class recreation stuff.</font>

106
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? That's so quick!</font>

107
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hon-chan, help me!</i></font>

108
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,610
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font size="28"><font face="Trebuchet MS"></font></font></b><i><font color="#88069e">THUD THUD THUD THUD</font></i></font>

109
00:05:01,610 --> 00:05:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please don't enter 
an I-know-nothing, I-don't-exist zone!</i></font>

110
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:04,870
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="14"><font face="Arial"></font></font></b>"I AM JUST BACKGROUND" MODE</font>

111
00:05:04,870 --> 00:05:09,870
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="28"><font face="Trebuchet MS"></font></font></b><i><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}THUD THUD</font></i></font>

112
00:05:04,870 --> 00:05:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I seem to be holding 
a conversation somehow,</i></font>

113
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I feel my pulse in my ears! 
I think I'm going crazy!</i></font>

114
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm pretty sure I'm happy, 
but I still want this time to go faster!</i></font>

115
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,120
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#9affd6">FWIP FWIP FWIP</font></font></b></font>

116
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,380
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#086a8f"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"></font></font></font></b>CONTRADICTORY</font>

117
00:05:14,790 --> 00:05:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're done!</font>

118
00:05:16,090 --> 00:05:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The two of you work so fast it's freaky.</font>

119
00:05:20,010 --> 00:05:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll drop these off 
in the staff room.</font>

120
00:05:20,010 --> 00:05:23,140
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font size="28"><font color="#29aa89">SHFF...</font></font></b></font>

121
00:05:23,140 --> 00:05:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want me to carry them?</font>

122
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Just sit there. Forever.</font>

123
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make it so I can't get up.</font>

124
00:05:29,350 --> 00:05:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hon-chan!</i></font>

125
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need something... to talk about.</i></font>

126
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The wind ensemble sure is 
practicing hard, huh?</font>

127
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sun has been 
setting earlier lately, hasn't it?</font>

128
00:05:53,290 --> 00:05:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Right?</font>

129
00:05:53,290 --> 00:05:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

130
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, um...</font>

131
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The group activity for our class trip...</font>

132
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishi-san, when your group decides where 
you're going, will you tell me in secret?</font>

133
00:06:09,850 --> 00:06:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

134
00:06:11,230 --> 00:06:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

135
00:06:12,230 --> 00:06:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should ask why or what for.</i></font>

136
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No.</i></font>

137
00:06:15,980 --> 00:06:20,730
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b>{\an8}IT'S NOT LIKE I HAVE ABSOLUTELY NO IDEA</font>

138
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't do that.</i></font>

139
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should be honest. Honest.</i></font>

140
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I understand and will do so.</font>

141
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's crazy polite.</font>

142
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where's Yamada?</font>

143
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:36,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He left with everyone from his class.</font>

144
00:06:36,250 --> 00:06:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear. I'm sorry.</font>

145
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't have to wait. 
You could've left with him.</font>

146
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm already over capacity.</font>

147
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're shrinking.</font>

148
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's certain, then.</font>

149
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

150
00:06:48,930 --> 00:06:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada, where were you?</font>

151
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went and helped next door.</font>

152
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

153
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today, I'm the only one who's been 
weirdly self-conscious. I'm a disgrace.</i></font>

154
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

155
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">before a class trip, 
the number of couples increases, right?</font>

156
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Really?</font>

157
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's to take full advantage 
of the free time.</font>

158
00:07:06,570 --> 00:07:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Phrasing.</font>

159
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki, Tani-kun, 
what're you going to do?</font>

160
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:10,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

161
00:07:10,910 --> 00:07:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, yeah, what should we do?</font>

162
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:17,120
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#990181"><font size="24"><font face="Trebuchet MS">AWKWARD</font></font></font></b></font>

163
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Suzuki, are you still acting 
like that with Tani-kun?</font>

164
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What? Acting like what, exactly?</font>

165
00:07:20,130 --> 00:07:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Highly suspiciously.</font>

166
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sus—</font>

167
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today just happens to be 
that sort of day, that's all!</font>

168
00:07:25,170 --> 00:07:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of day is that?</font>

169
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm usually more clever than this!</font>

170
00:07:28,890 --> 00:07:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun is laughing, though.</font>

171
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

172
00:07:31,850 --> 00:07:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

173
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san, I'd like to spend my 
free time with you.</font>

174
00:07:36,310 --> 00:07:37,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sudden!</font>

175
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Well said, Tani!</font>

176
00:07:39,810 --> 00:07:40,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

177
00:07:40,810 --> 00:07:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy for you.</font>

178
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, please go right ahead.</font>

179
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:49,030
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#77572e"></font></b><font size="12">TRAIN-TO-SCHOOL GROUP</font></font>

180
00:07:44,650 --> 00:07:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Suzuki and Tani 
seem kind of weird today?</font>

181
00:07:47,610 --> 00:07:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Did they?</font>

182
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, as long as they don't say anything,</font>

183
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can leave it alone, right?</font>

184
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I guess so.</font>

185
00:07:53,910 --> 00:07:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? Are we going to 
head home together like this?</i></font>

186
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna stop by the convenience store.</font>

187
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sure.</font>

188
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, then...</font>

189
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice! What should I buy?</font>

190
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seriously?</i></font>

191
00:08:11,970 --> 00:08:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azuma!</font>

192
00:08:13,180 --> 00:08:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Morning!</font>

193
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kawasaki! Morning.</font>

194
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did your group decide 
where to go during the class trip?</font>

195
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. We haven't even decided 
on our groups yet.</font>

196
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? This late?</font>

197
00:08:23,650 --> 00:08:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We decided a whole bunch of stuff.
It's exhausting.</font>

198
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:32,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole class has a 
"I don't wanna say the wrong thing" aura,</font>

199
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so no one gives a single opinion.</font>

200
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:43,460
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font color="#d7dbf0"><font size="16">CLASS TRIP</font></font></font>

201
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:43,460
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font color="#d7dbf0"><font size="16">PICKING GROUPS</font></font></font>

202
00:08:36,450 --> 00:08:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Then we'll decide the groups 
by lottery. Is that okay?</font>

203
00:08:41,170 --> 00:08:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, we'll do it by lottery.</font>

204
00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anywhere you wanna go?</font>

205
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah.</font>

206
00:08:46,710 --> 00:08:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, no. Nowhere in particular.</font>

207
00:08:49,970 --> 00:08:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm begging you! 
Please give your opinion just a bit!</font>

208
00:08:53,430 --> 00:08:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then they say that 
I decided everything behind their backs!</font>

209
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't skip making decisions 
or giving your opinion, then!</font>

210
00:08:59,690 --> 00:09:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Calm down. Calm down.</font>

211
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:01,230
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font color="#ed5009"><font size="28">ARGHHHH</font></font></b></font>

212
00:09:02,230 --> 00:09:04,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did good work.</font>

213
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, should we assign groups
by lottery, or let everyone pick?</font>

214
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be better 
if we got to pick, right?</font>

215
00:09:14,450 --> 00:09:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To be honest, I think 
 a lottery is way better.</i></font>

216
00:09:18,540 --> 00:09:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, I fumbled planning the class trip,
so we're going to decide stuff fast now.</font>

217
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it! I thought our class 
seemed way behind!</font>

218
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, form groups of two to 
three of all girls or all boys.</font>

219
00:09:31,170 --> 00:09:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we'll combine each boy group with a 
girl group to form a group of five to six.</font>

220
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How slapdash can you be?</font>

221
00:09:36,890 --> 00:09:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Uh-oh. Two to three people.</i></font>

222
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:43,400
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#d43dcf">{\an8}HANG OUT A LOT</font></font></b></font>

223
00:09:39,890 --> 00:09:43,400
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#5d53e2">HANG-OUT GROUP
(+SUZUKI)</font></font></b></font>

224
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:41,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20"><font color="#2acc2d">ALWAYS TOGETHER</font></font></font></b></font>

225
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:42,270
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20"><font color="#2acc2d">ALWAYS TOGETHER</font></font></font></b></font>

226
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,400
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20"><font color="#2acc2d">ALWAYS TOGETHER</font></font></font></b></font>

227
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I do? 
Is there anyone left over?</i></font>

228
00:09:45,060 --> 00:09:47,270
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font size="24"><font color="#ee368e">GLANCE GLANCE GLANCE</font></font></b></font>

229
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:52,900
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20"><font color="#fee9ff"></font></font></font></b>(I'LL GO TO A DIFFERENT GROUP)</font>

230
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:54,660
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24"><font color="#ffe8fd"></font></font></font></b>(GOT IT!)</font>

231
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did she understand?</i></font>

232
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,660
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#6b5088">DID SHE UNDERSTAND...?</font></font></font></b></font>

233
00:09:55,660 --> 00:09:57,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teacher! Can we have a group of four?</font>

234
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No! That's not it!</i></font>

235
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sure.</font>

236
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That easy?</font>

237
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just talk it out amongst yourselves 
and make it work.</font>

238
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:04,920
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#eefe37"><font size="20">IF IT GETS DONE,
ANYTHING'S FINE.</font></font></b></font>

239
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,920
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#e9edef"><font size="24">IN THE END...</font></font></b></font>

240
00:10:05,290 --> 00:10:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end...</font>

241
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

242
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:09,420
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f8fc9b">YAY!</font></b></font>

243
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,920
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f7a8f3"><font size="24">SIGH...</font></font></b></font>

244
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The truth is, I've already 
bought sightseeing magazines.</font>

245
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:16,600
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24"><font color="#f8dd85">TABIPPLE</font></font></font></b></font>

246
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:13,930
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#ffffff">FALL</font></font></b></font>

247
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:13,930
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="32"><font color="#fdff75">BAM</font></font></font></b></font>

248
00:10:15,010 --> 00:10:16,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Well done!</font>

249
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:21,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#5d8fea">{\an8}FWIP FWIP FWIP</font></font></b></font>

250
00:10:17,470 --> 00:10:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm glad I didn't have to be 
awkwardly considerate.</i></font>

251
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,730
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f9ff83"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="30">...HUH?</font></font></font></b></font>

252
00:10:22,430 --> 00:10:23,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, no, no.</i></font>

253
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:28,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I worry about every little thing 
the whole trip, what'll happen?</i></font>

254
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since I started high school, 
it's like I'm in a group, but also not.</i></font>

255
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I make sure not to get too attached, so I 
can go anywhere, and I keep my distance.</i></font>

256
00:10:38,410 --> 00:10:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's easiest when it's just me, 
or me and one other person.</i></font>

257
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, maybe my social circle 
is too small?</i></font>

258
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:47,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f4c6ee"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20">{\an7}YEAR 1, SPRING</font></font></font></b></font>

259
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you! 
What middle school are you from?</font>

260
00:10:44,290 --> 00:10:47,170
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="16"></font></font></b><font color="#d057a3">1. KAWASAKI</font></font>

261
00:10:47,210 --> 00:10:49,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f8f9e0"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20">{\an7}YEAR 2, SPRING</font></font></font></b></font>

262
00:10:47,330 --> 00:10:49,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="16"></font></font></b><font color="#800da4">2. SUZUKI</font></font>

263
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

264
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:52,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not that I'm shy around strangers,</i></font>

265
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but for some reason, I tend 
to get cautious at weird times.</i></font>

266
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:59,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet it's so easy 
to pester Taira for no reason.</font>

267
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't pester me for no reason.</font>

268
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's this coming from?</font>

269
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just saying, "Taira is 
so easy to talk to." That's all.</font>

270
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

271
00:11:07,730 --> 00:11:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, of course I am, 
from your perspective.</font>

272
00:11:10,610 --> 00:11:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

273
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:13,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no reason for you 
to be nervous, right?</font>

274
00:11:13,650 --> 00:11:14,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

275
00:11:14,700 --> 00:11:18,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, "What if I say this?" 
Or, "I want to look good here."</font>

276
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Worrying about stuff
like status and feelings</font>

277
00:11:20,330 --> 00:11:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">versus it not affecting anything
if you mess up...</font>

278
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the comfort level is different.</font>

279
00:11:25,210 --> 00:11:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that I know if you 
worry about that stuff, though.</font>

280
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what?</font>

281
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means...</font>

282
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira, it's as if I totally 
look down on you!</font>

283
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:37,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's because that's the truth!</font>

284
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, but when I think about it...</i></font>

285
00:11:38,590 --> 00:11:40,800
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font color="#d7dbf0"><font size="16">CLASS TRIP</font></font></font>

286
00:11:38,590 --> 00:11:40,800
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b></b><font color="#d7dbf0"><font size="16">PICKING GROUPS</font></font></font>

287
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:41,300
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#befff4"><font size="24">SILENCE...</font></font></b></font>

288
00:11:38,930 --> 00:11:40,890
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="28"><font color="#bbffc1">SENSE OF ANXIETY</font></font></b></font>

289
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:47,060
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20"><font color="#f8dd85">TABIPPLE</font></font></font></b></font>

290
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:47,060
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#ffffff">FALL</font></font></b></font>

291
00:11:41,810 --> 00:11:47,060
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="28">{\an8}<font color="#fcbce8">NO SENSE OF ANXIETY</font></font></b></font>

292
00:11:41,970 --> 00:11:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That could explain it.</font>

293
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

294
00:11:44,850 --> 00:11:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, not the looking down on you thing.</font>

295
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Anxiety.</i></font>

296
00:11:51,110 --> 00:11:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>About what?</i></font>

297
00:11:54,860 --> 00:11:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I have work today, so...</font>

298
00:11:56,900 --> 00:11:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure! Work hard!</font>

299
00:12:00,490 --> 00:12:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder...</i></font>

300
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>what am I afraid of?</i></font>

301
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azuma!</font>

302
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you free on Saturday?</font>

303
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

304
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you guys talking about?</font>

305
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just asking her 
to hang out on Saturday.</font>

306
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I'll totally go!</font>

307
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azuma, you can go, right?</font>

308
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm interested in that guy. 
Will you help me?</font>

309
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

310
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:26,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azuma, you know I like him, right?</font>

311
00:12:26,890 --> 00:12:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's help her out.
We're friends, right?</font>

312
00:12:31,230 --> 00:12:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess it's fine. 
It's not like I hate them.</i></font>

313
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being used... and getting swept along, 
even though I know what's going on.</i></font>

314
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If that's true...</i></font>

315
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that has nothing to do with now, does it?</i></font>

316
00:12:56,000 --> 00:13:01,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then, I think I had even less of my 
own thoughts and will than I do now.</i></font>

317
00:13:01,590 --> 00:13:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't skip making decisions 
or giving your opinion, then!</font>

318
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're so right, Kawasaki.</i></font>

319
00:13:08,230 --> 00:13:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Azuma!</font>

320
00:13:11,140 --> 00:13:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoohoo! Good work today!</font>

321
00:13:13,650 --> 00:13:16,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nabesato, this isn't 
the way you go home, is it?</font>

322
00:13:16,070 --> 00:13:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. We thought we'd go shopping, 
maybe get a few things for the class trip.</font>

323
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're headed the same way, 
so can we walk together?</font>

324
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:24,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

325
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't go this way much, 
so it feels brand new.</font>

326
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, I heard a taiyaki shop opened up in 
front of the station. Let's stop by later.</font>

327
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you just eat a snack?</font>

328
00:13:34,330 --> 00:13:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't there a second stomach for taiyaki?</font>

329
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never heard that.</font>

330
00:13:36,130 --> 00:13:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Can I go shopping with you?</font>

331
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! There it is!</font>

332
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to a drugstore. 
Is there one you like?</font>

333
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're thinking of going 
to the one by the statue.</font>

334
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:47,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one by the station's 
south entrance is well stocked.</font>

335
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

336
00:13:48,930 --> 00:13:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to buy face wash 
and moisturizer for a travel kit.</font>

337
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azuma, do you know of any good ones?</font>

338
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe buy containers 
and fill them with your stuff?</font>

339
00:13:55,940 --> 00:13:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, good idea.</font>

340
00:13:56,820 --> 00:14:00,690
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#625656"><font size="24">TEA</font></font></b></font>

341
00:13:56,820 --> 00:14:00,690
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#625656"><font size="24">TEA</font></font></b></font>

342
00:13:56,820 --> 00:14:00,690
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="12"></font></font></b>FOR SALE AT THE HOTEL SHOP</font>

343
00:13:56,860 --> 00:13:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe they'll have 
some where we stay?</font>

344
00:13:59,030 --> 00:14:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

345
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this is the first chance we've had to 
see Azuma without makeup! I can't wait!</font>

346
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a little curious, too.</font>

347
00:14:06,410 --> 00:14:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like there's no difference, 
but it's not enough to get a laugh,</font>

348
00:14:09,950 --> 00:14:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so don't get too excited.</font>

349
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that mean?</font>

350
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:25,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="12"></font></font></b>TAIYAKI</font>

351
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

352
00:14:23,430 --> 00:14:25,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like they're eating taiyaki!</font>

353
00:14:25,470 --> 00:14:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so jealous!</font>

354
00:14:25,470 --> 00:14:28,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#886d54">O D E N</font></b></font>

355
00:14:26,970 --> 00:14:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go home.</font>

356
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class trip!</font>

357
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class trip, day 1: Hands-on learning!</font>

358
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an3}<font size="20"><font color="#a12565">DAY 1: HANDS-ON LEARNING</font></font></b></font>

359
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an7}<font size="8"><font color="#f1cfdd"><font face="Arial">EVERYONE SPLITS UP TO TAKE
THE COURSE THEY CHOSE</font></font></font></b></font>

360
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#a1026e"><font size="12">PAINTING 1</font></font></b></font>

361
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#a1026e"><font size="12">PAINTING 2</font></font></b></font>

362
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an7}<font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="28"><font color="#f2503b">TR<font color="#f88de1">IP <font color="#fbffca">GUIDE</font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

363
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#a1026e"><font size="12">MAKING
JAPANESE
SWEETS</font></font></b></font>

364
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#a1026e"><font size="12">CERAMICS</font></font></b></font>

365
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:39,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#a1026e"><font size="12">KUMIHIMO BRAIDING</font></font></b></font>

366
00:14:40,230 --> 00:14:43,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, everyone gather up 
for each activity separately!</font>

367
00:14:43,780 --> 00:14:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I could've done Japanese 
sweets instead of ceramics.</font>

368
00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:48,410
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#695241"></font></b><font size="12">CERAMICS GROUP</font></font>

369
00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:48,410
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#505b65"></font></b><font size="12">PAINTING GROUP</font></font>

370
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't something you can keep better?</font>

371
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:53,790
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#bf7d53"></font></b><font size="12">JAPANESE SWEETS
GROUP</font></font>

372
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got the Japanese sweets 
experience through R-P-S!</font>

373
00:14:51,370 --> 00:14:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll eat enough for our 
fallen comrades!</font>

374
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't kill me off!</font>

375
00:14:55,170 --> 00:14:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can only eat what you've made.</font>

376
00:14:58,340 --> 00:14:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Nissan!</font>

377
00:14:58,590 --> 00:15:01,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="12"><font face="Arial"></font></font></b>JAPANESE SWEETS
MAKING VENUE</font>

378
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san.</font>

379
00:15:03,010 --> 00:15:05,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The pretty girl! Yamada's friend!</i></font>

380
00:15:05,050 --> 00:15:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The unrealistic couple 
Nisshi told me about.</i></font>

381
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay if we sit here?</font>

382
00:15:08,970 --> 00:15:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do.</font>

383
00:15:10,010 --> 00:15:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Nice to meet you. 
Sorry for intruding on your table.</font>

384
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:15,020
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><i><font color="#f3f6d1">SMILE</font></i></font></b></font>

385
00:15:13,890 --> 00:15:15,020
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#cb1a7b">(NEUTRAL ATTITUDE)</font></b></font>

386
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Nice to meet you.</font>

387
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh! She's adorable!</i></font>

388
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and sit down.</font>

389
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What an amusing woman.</i></font>

390
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You take this and go like this...</font>

391
00:15:23,530 --> 00:15:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The teacher makes it 
look so easy, but this is hard.</font>

392
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, you're so good! 
Did you practice in secret?</font>

393
00:15:31,950 --> 00:15:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I didn't.</font>

394
00:15:33,540 --> 00:15:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then why can you do it?</font>

395
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

396
00:15:36,290 --> 00:15:40,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Why? I'm just doing it how I was shown." 
He's that kind of character, huh?</font>

397
00:15:40,590 --> 00:15:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

398
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry. It slipped out a little.</font>

399
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right! Nissan, where is 
your group going tomorrow?</font>

400
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:47,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's...</font>

401
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in that order. Right, Hon-chan?</font>

402
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

403
00:15:52,350 --> 00:15:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's pretty much the same as us!</font>

404
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might end up 
in the same place!</font>

405
00:15:56,730 --> 00:15:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hang on.</i></font>

406
00:15:58,060 --> 00:15:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about here?</font>

407
00:15:59,900 --> 00:16:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to go! I'm in! I'm in!</font>

408
00:16:01,650 --> 00:16:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds good.</font>

409
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No objections!</font>

410
00:16:03,270 --> 00:16:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it's decided!</font>

411
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

412
00:16:05,530 --> 00:16:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-That guy...</i></font>

413
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:10,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He arranged it around Nissan, right?</i></font>

414
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:15,700
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#beff8d">GRIN...</font></font></b></font>

415
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we see each other, 
I'd love to take a picture!</font>

416
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Um, I'd love to!</font>

417
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:15,700
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#eb3db0"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="16">I'D LOVE
TO...!!!!</font></font></font></b></font>

418
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:20,960
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#c00587">BIG ROOM</font></font></b></font>

419
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the baths start with group 1, 
then group 7 is way later, right?</font>

420
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to play cards while we wait?</font>

421
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! I love the classics.</font>

422
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It has to be, right? But still...</font>

423
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought dominoes, too.</font>

424
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Right?</font>

425
00:16:30,220 --> 00:16:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that's unusual.</font>

426
00:16:32,010 --> 00:16:33,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Suzuki?</font>

427
00:16:33,470 --> 00:16:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

428
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:35,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki, are you and Tani dating?</font>

429
00:16:35,970 --> 00:16:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

430
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but...</font>

431
00:16:38,230 --> 00:16:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Now?</font>

432
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The two of them are always together,</font>

433
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I guess this is how people see them.</font>

434
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:45,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were wondering which it was.</font>

435
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Suzuki is with a guy, 
there's no special meaning, right?</font>

436
00:16:46,610 --> 00:16:50,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="20"><font color="#ffffcc">EXAMPLE</font></font></font></b></font>

437
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

438
00:16:50,990 --> 00:17:02,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24"><font color="#f8fdbc">SQUEE SQUEE
<font size="28"><font color="#f49ad5">YAY YAY</font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

439
00:16:50,990 --> 00:16:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, which one of you confessed first?</font>

440
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:54,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What sparked it?</font>

441
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you actually talk to each other?</font>

442
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I totally get it. You just want to 
press her with lots of questions.</font>

443
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How nostalgic.</font>

444
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's acting like a veteran.</font>

445
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How far have you gone?</font>

446
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?!</font>

447
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're really going for it, huh?</font>

448
00:17:05,750 --> 00:17:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When they called you two at the 
culture festival, what were you doing?</font>

449
00:17:09,090 --> 00:17:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And also...</font>

450
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does Tani even have that kind of desire?</font>

451
00:17:12,390 --> 00:17:14,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly! We're closed for business!</font>

452
00:17:14,220 --> 00:17:16,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, dear. She's closed.</font>

453
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How far?</i></font>

454
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those things that everyone's 
excitedly imagining...</i></font>

455
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not a single one has happened!</i></font>

456
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:27,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Group 7! Head to the baths.</font>

457
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I really think about it, 
up to this point...</i></font>

458
00:17:32,660 --> 00:17:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I may have been pressing him a lot.</i></font>

459
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,780
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#f7f4d4">{\an8}I WOULD LIKE
<font color="#db8dbc">TO HUG...</font></font></font></b></font>

460
00:17:34,530 --> 00:17:35,910
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#89bed6">{\an8}STARE...</font></font></font></b></font>

461
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:38,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he'll take my hand and stuff, so...</i></font>

462
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:38,830
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><i><font color="#e25dcc"><font face="Trebuchet MS">{\an8}BA-DUMP</font></font></i></font></b></font>

463
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I'm totally honest, 
I want him to start stuff even more!</i></font>

464
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When Suzuki is with a guy, 
there's no special meaning, right?</font>

465
00:17:48,670 --> 00:17:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was I putting out too much of a 
"non-romantic character" vibe?</i></font>

466
00:17:52,180 --> 00:17:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Suzuki!</font>

467
00:17:54,180 --> 00:17:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you are.</font>

468
00:17:55,260 --> 00:17:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azu...</font>

469
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the troubled expression?</font>

470
00:18:00,850 --> 00:18:02,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want there to be developments.</font>

471
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

472
00:18:04,940 --> 00:18:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess... I want that kind of appeal.</font>

473
00:18:04,940 --> 00:18:17,700
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#f6f5bb">GURGLE
GURGLE
GURGLE</font></font></font></b></font>

474
00:18:08,650 --> 00:18:10,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki, you're more than cute enough.</font>

475
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azu, this "cute" of yours
isn't how I want to be thought of.</font>

476
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:17,700
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="20"></font></b><font face="Arial">{\an8}<font color="#9648a4">NOT DENYING IT</font></font></font>

477
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... I mean, it's not something 
you should rush into in a panic.</font>

478
00:18:22,330 --> 00:18:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, the peak 
is everything that leads up to it.</font>

479
00:18:25,130 --> 00:18:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, slow is fine, isn't it?</font>

480
00:18:26,790 --> 00:18:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? But...</font>

481
00:18:29,210 --> 00:18:33,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="20"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#f6f5bb">GURGLE
GURGLE
GURGLE</font></font></font></b></font>

482
00:18:29,210 --> 00:18:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I'd at least like to 
smooch sometime soon.</font>

483
00:18:33,470 --> 00:18:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Smooch.</i></font>

484
00:18:33,470 --> 00:18:35,720
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#ca6b8b">SMOOCH...</font></font></b></font>

485
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think I could... you know, give 
off a "good woman" vibe like you do?</font>

486
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, if I had to say,
I'm more the "nobody really cares woman."</font>

487
00:18:45,230 --> 00:18:50,730
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><i><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#d5a6f7">I'M NOT A
GOOD EXAMPLE...</font></font></i></font></b></font>

488
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's blinding. Someone save me.</i></font>

489
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were smart to bring a hair dryer.</font>

490
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Azuma, your eyebrows 
seem kinda different.</font>

491
00:18:59,370 --> 00:19:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, with this lustrous, flowing hair 
and fresh-out-of-the-bath appearance,</font>

492
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do hope I see Tani-kun!</font>

493
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't wait until morning?</font>

494
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be over in a few minutes.</font>

495
00:19:08,250 --> 00:19:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't I just run into him at the entrance?</font>

496
00:19:10,750 --> 00:19:13,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#bb2490"><font size="16">TINTED</font></font></b></font>

497
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:13,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want him to see the natural me, 
right out of the bath!</font>

498
00:19:11,130 --> 00:19:13,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#bb2490"><font size="16">COLORED LIP BALM</font></font></b></font>

499
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:13,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#bb2490"><font size="16">MINERAL
FOUNDATION</font></font></b></font>

500
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though it's a fake no-makeup face?</font>

501
00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look!</font>

502
00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:23,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#cfff85">{\an8}SNEAK...</font></b></font>

503
00:19:20,930 --> 00:19:22,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you the embarrassed ones?</font>

504
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's totally fine to be introverted.</font>

505
00:19:25,850 --> 00:19:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to make fun.</font>

506
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where's Tani-kun?</font>

507
00:19:28,610 --> 00:19:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the key, 
so he should be there, right?</font>

508
00:19:37,570 --> 00:19:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoohoo.</font>

509
00:19:39,530 --> 00:19:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada said you'd probably be over here.</font>

510
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,910
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#bc48c8"><i>{\an9}THUMP
THUMP
THUMP</i></font></font></b></font>

511
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:46,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, I'm a little different 
than usual, aren't I?</font>

512
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. My heart skipped a beat.</font>

513
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:53,050
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#ed5c80"><i>{\an7}THUMP THUMP THUMP</i></font></font></b></font>

514
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A perfect score? Suddenly, 
the solution I wanted has arrived.</i></font>

515
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were someone else, 
so I was surprised.</font>

516
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:55,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, I had it wrong! It was fear!</i></font>

517
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:55,050
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#d8db7f">OH NO...!!</font></font></b></font>

518
00:19:55,050 --> 00:19:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it was you, Suzuki-san, 
so I felt better.</font>

519
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

520
00:19:59,050 --> 00:20:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right!</font>

521
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:07,060
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#740083">CHANGING THE SUBJECT
TO HIDE EMBARRASSMENT</font></font></b></font>

522
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, you ended up in a big room 
with a bunch of noisy people.</font>

523
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay? It's kind of hilarious.</font>

524
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't find hilarity in this.</font>

525
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They seemed to be having fun 
playing a card game.</font>

526
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you join in?</font>

527
00:20:10,190 --> 00:20:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know the rules, 
so I just watched.</font>

528
00:20:13,320 --> 00:20:16,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like fun! 
That goofy way guys get excited.</font>

529
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:20,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But not long ago, you probably
 would've turned away from all of it.</font>

530
00:20:20,110 --> 00:20:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both the room and the game.</font>

531
00:20:21,410 --> 00:20:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not...</font>

532
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's probably true.</font>

533
00:20:24,330 --> 00:20:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

534
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is true.</font>

535
00:20:26,870 --> 00:20:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spending so much time 
with other people like this...</font>

536
00:20:29,580 --> 00:20:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A year ago, I'd never have
 imagined myself doing it.</font>

537
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which way is more fun?</font>

538
00:20:36,170 --> 00:20:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think it's about 
which is more fun.</font>

539
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

540
00:20:38,380 --> 00:20:39,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ea4095"><font size="16">OH...?</font></font></b></font>

541
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never felt particularly 
dissatisfied with anything.</font>

542
00:20:43,100 --> 00:20:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, but that's the part of Tani-kun 
 I fell in love with in the first place.</i></font>

543
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:49,310
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#fbfebc"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24">SOLITARY</font></font></font></b></font>

544
00:20:48,850 --> 00:20:49,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just...</font>

545
00:20:50,940 --> 00:20:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">now I have confusion and worries 
that I didn't have when I was alone.</font>

546
00:20:56,230 --> 00:20:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And things I wouldn't have 
known otherwise.</font>

547
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are probably still a lot more.</font>

548
00:21:01,780 --> 00:21:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad that I'm not 
still ignorant of those things.</font>

549
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, it's not "which one," it's "both"?</font>

550
00:21:11,170 --> 00:21:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. And that's why...</font>

551
00:21:14,210 --> 00:21:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I met you.</font>

552
00:21:20,130 --> 00:21:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta— Yuu— Tani-kun!</font>

553
00:21:23,010 --> 00:21:28,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>U-Up until just now, 
I was only thinking of wicked things!</i></font>

554
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so embarrassed!</i></font>

555
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuusuke-kun...</font>

556
00:21:46,530 --> 00:21:47,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you.</font>

557
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miyu...</font>

558
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Okay! Time to get back 
to our rooms, right?!</font>

559
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you tomorrow! 
Have fun in that room of yours!</font>

560
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:05,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no need to get weirdly panicked!</i></font>

561
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so...</font>

562
00:22:13,980 --> 00:22:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they stayed up long 
into the night of their first day.</font>

563
00:22:13,980 --> 00:22:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yay! Yay!</font>

564
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:19,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm looking forward to tomorrow!</font>

